    "The application of this search resulted in a total of 235 articles.",
    "These publications were subjected to an abstract reading filter that allowed the identification of 200 documents dealing with the subject matter consulted, rejecting n=35 documents from this first screening (Figure 1).",
    "The main reasons for exclusion were, as follows:",
    "1. not being related to the subject matter, 2. being in a language other than English, Spanish, or Portuguese, and 3. being indexed in the Social Sciences area but being technical articles, mainly in computer sciences.",
    "Table 1 presents the categories of analysis applied to the sample of 200 articles."
